OL,5,
OL,6,FAll audiences deserve to be served by
OL,7,Fthe BBC. Everyone should get value from
OL,8,Ftheir licence fee.
OL,10,FBut surely that means trying to serve
OL,11,Fall audiences with something of
OL,12,Foriginality and value.
OL,14,FThis programme ` at least superficially
OL,15,F` seemed derivative. If AI was used to
